Usage: SET STATUS_NOTIFY_START_VAR <Status line text>
  The contents of STATUS_NOTIFY_START_VAR are placed in the
  STATUS_NOTIFY format before window number that triggered REPWORD.
  This can be used to highlight windows where REPWORD is triggered
  with a different color.

See also:
  SET STATUS_NOTIFY_VAR, SET STATUS_NOTIFY_END_VAR,
  REPWORD
